title: data analyst
text: Data analysts are responsible for looking at data and analyzing how the data can impact best business practices.

title: data engineer
text: Incorrect: Data engineers certainly need a lot of experience and technical skills. They are a key role in any data science team. However, they will often serve another person or team in delivering quality data sets. Typically data engineers are not creating visualizations

title: data architect
text: Incorrect: Data architects define how an organization's data is stored, consumed, integrated and managed across its different systems and applications.
